TECH-INFUSED BUSINESS DEGREE PROGRAMS








FROM A FOREVER FORWARD UNIVERSITY





































 





    BUSINESS LEADERSHIP AND TECHNOLOGY SKILLS FOR TODAY'S HIGH-TECH, GLOBAL MARKETPLACE
  


Since 1931, DeVry University has harnessed the power of technology to innovate education. We bring our founder’s perspective to education. We try new things, look at challenges in new ways, and vigorously question precedent. Then and now, we’ve helped our students understand the ever-changing world.Today, DeVry University continues Herman DeVry’s spirit of innovation and inquiry and curiosity and forward-thinking. We teach how technology integrates people, process, data and devices to solve modern business problems. We show a sharp, clear picture of the modern landscape so students can see how to advance in it.
Technology is at our core and embedded in our programs – because it’s at the core of business, healthcare and tech, everywhere. Our students dig deeper into understanding technology’s role in all things…so they can be ready for whatever comes next.



Study Business Administration at DeVry University



Whether you’re just getting started or have previous college credits, DeVry University has a business degree program to meet your needs. No matter which program you choose- Accounting, Business Administration, Management or Technical Management -  you’ll have the option to focus your studies in areas such as Accounting, Project Management, Entrepreneurship, Sales and Marketing, Health Services Management and more. For more information on our programs, take the next step by filling out the simple form on this page.


